T02D2818:169b-0: @169b * // 'phags pa thugs rje chen po thugs rje khros pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2818:169b-1: ma lus yon tan rgya mtsho'i mthas klas pas //
T02D2818:169b-2: 'gro ba'i don du rmad byung shin tu grags //
T02D2818:169b-3: stobs bcu lha dang mi lus rnam rgyal ba //
T02D2818:169b-4: gtso bo nyid gcig thugs rjes khros la 'dud //
T02D2818:169b-5: snying rje shes rab 'od gsal shes rab dag / gnyis med gnyis su rab ston pa //
T02D2818:169b-6: de ming thugs rje chen po'o //
T02D2818:169b-7: gdul bya'i don mthong rang bzhin dang //
T02D2818:169b-8: cig shos zhi dang zhi bral dang //
T02D2818:169b-9: gdul bya rnams kyi don phyir ni //
T02D2818:169b-10: dpal ldan bzang khros par snang ba //
T02D2818:169b-11: nyin mtshan zla ba dkar dang nag / dul ba dang ni gdug pa dang //
T02D2818:169b-12: gnyis la gnyis mdzad mgon po mchog / cha lugs gnyis kyis gnyis bya'o //
T02D2818:169b-13: bdag nyid rdo rje chen po yi //
T02D2818:169b-14: bsrung bas gzi byin bskyed pa'i rjes //
T02D2818:169b-15: de yi gnas dang lus bskyab pa'ang //
T02D2818:169b-16: ji bzhin cig car thog thag brtag / aom a'a:hr'i:h'um /
T02D2818:169b-20: rgya gram gzugs kyis bzhad pa'i zhal //
T02D2818:169b-21: gnam lcags rgyun sgra sngags kyi lces //
T02D2818:169b-22: bsrung ba bya dang brlag bya ba //
T02D2818:169b-23: mtshan ma'i rnal 'byor las gzhan min //
